title: Garmin city navigator north america NT 2008
description:
* Premium maps contain full coverage throughout the U.S., Canada and Puerto Rico including metropolitan and rural areas

   * Includes detailed maps containing highways, interstates, business and residential roads with attributes such as turn restrictions, roundabout guidance, speed categories and other navigation features

   * Displays nearly 6 million points of interest such as:

         o food and drink

         o lodging

         o attractions

         o entertainment

         o shopping

         o emergency services

         o post offices

         o gas stations and more

   * Automatically creates point-to-point routes in MapSourceÃ‚Â® and on your NT compatible GPS, see the product compatibility list on the right.

   * Postal code support for Canada

   * Enhances pronunciation data for compatible GPS devices that can speak street names (example: "Turn right on Main St."). Your GPS device must be able to speak street names to use this data.
